{"type": "article", "id": 53231, "title": "肯德基推出王子大婚炸鸡桶，Gucci Bloom 的手绘稿挺好看 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-05-16T03:49:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 45908, "name": "哈里王子"}, {"id": 3790, "name": "卡地亚"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180516112402ZDX8OQtpkAfdmzeE.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://weibo.com/bolonsunglasses?from=feed&amp;loc=at&amp;nick=BOLON%E6%9A%B4%E9%BE%99%E7%9C%BC%E9%95%9C\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>BOLON 眼镜宣布王俊凯成为全新品牌代言人</b></a>，同时发布了限量礼盒预售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516104355uXA6Y2wepJt7L8Uq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NjYzNDg1Mw==&amp;mid=2651724969&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d9dba51842e5a40bec17751725192cb5&amp;chksm=bd1cf5238a6b7c35f91487275fff1d5f3f94ea6deb6e331bb12b8ae5a4ee8d2896034c741e6d&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=051592AirsbvCnqUDpuqTWf6&amp;key=a088dd6918b80ea0948589f345143d588665c5e416a86590f8532c19173a58b9ed6f99864bc548c056426c64aaf4aded0bfc19ff2ad85472242054672e9a3f3e59af83b6631a7cef63538491c8f1b342&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.13.4+build(17E199)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=ULkLekI8IeoSciXdDuS74A22x6kZV4uWoqkKVYQCnS5J1bRHJk3GO6Xc7cJHa4U8\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>7-Eleven X 同道大叔推出幸福单人泡面碗</b></a>，也是通过集点换购的方式，5 月 16 日在上海和浙江地区的门店发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516100756PvX4DdISgfAHKYQj.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.741811\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mashable.com/2018/05/14/kfc-prince-harry-meghan-markle/#ahjIIJJ9Akqs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为庆祝英国哈里王子大婚，肯德基推出 50 份限量版皇家婚礼桶</b></a>，仅在距离新皇室夫妇游行路线附近 1.3 英里的温莎分店出售。炸鸡桶的一边印有金色的肯德基标签，另一边则印有一段标语：“我们宣布这是值得庆祝的一天，这是一个喜庆的日子……还有炸鸡。”哈里王子和梅根将在 5 月 19 日举行婚礼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516103157vyaW7fOqurQRkxbm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.567873\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/05/15/converse-miley-cyrus-collection-campaign/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>继去年 “Yes to All” campaign 后 ，匡威与麦莉再度合作，推出最新匡威 × Miley 系列</b></a>，麦莉还邀请了真爱粉共同拍摄产品宣传画册，可以说是实力宠粉了。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516104848TMn5dzvCGV13Fk6X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739269\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516104920GSA5q8YXVeF7sZ13.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.650794\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/27223.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>黄轩为卡地亚拍摄微电影广告《爱若初见》</b></a>，感觉在片中化身话痨……黄轩在卡地亚的代言级别为品牌挚友。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=t06533c3fb5&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44375\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为了具象地描绘出淡香水的清香，GUCCI 邀请了 15 位来自世界各地的女性艺术家创作出她们对 Gucci Bloom 的初印象</b></a>，以 Instagram 为主要的传播平台。<br></p><p class=\"\">画风非常迥异，但都相当迷人。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516111019FeLmd9BEt2oOrQMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516111044lLqC48vVBabjk0rI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516111048FYoSTjdUZNHsixuI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.985000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180516111052yxBJq3KD1jStM2Ir.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44377\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>宜家台湾发布了三支短片，用反转手法拍摄了“在宜家上演的各种约会的小事”</b></a>。继 2016 年宜家出了约会二三事系列短片后，陆陆续续推出了很多关于“约会”的广告。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=u0652w4dnfh&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/44371\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>德国 Ergo 保险新广告挺有意思</b></a>，用音乐剧唱腔表现了肇事人的花式道歉，但如果道歉有用的话要保险公司干嘛呢……该赔还是得赔。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=m06548rzrld&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://adage.com/article/digital/china-facebook-s-largest-market/313524/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>中国成为 Facebook 仅次于美国的第二大广告市场</b></a>。根据 Pivotal Research 报告，尽管被禁止在中国运营，但 Facebook 的全球收入中有近 10％ 来自中国，约为 50 亿美元，仅次于美国市场。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://industry.caijing.com.cn/20180515/4453343.shtml\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>抖音上线店铺入口</b></a>，用户可以进入抖音达人的个人店铺，进行购物。这是自今年 3 月底，抖音提供外链淘宝的购物车后，在电商领域的又一次试水。<br></p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：GUCCI</p>"}